readme.text:
Genius Lyrics

[![npm](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/genius-lyrics)](https://npmjs.com/package/genius-lyrics) [![npm](https://img.shields.io/npm/dw/genius-lyrics)](https://npmjs.com/package/genius-lyrics) [![npm](https://img.shields.io/npm/l/genius-lyrics)](https://npmjs.com/package/genius-lyrics) [![Documentation](https://github.com/zyrouge/node-genius-lyrics/actions/workflows/docs.yml/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://github.com/zyrouge/node-genius-lyrics/actions/workflows/docs.yml) ## Whats is this? Just a simple lyrics fetcher that uses [Genius](https://genius.com). This also has official API implementations. ## Installation

```js
const Genius = require("genius-lyrics");
const Client = new Genius.Client("top-secret-optional-key"); // Scrapes if no key is provided
```

```ts
import Genius from "genius-lyrics";
const Client = new Genius.Client("top-secret-optional-key"); // Scrapes if no key is provided
```
